name: VoidLoop.Rotate(horizontal)
description:
Echoes of harsh experiences left behind
Cathartic journey forward into the mind
Physical limitations of the body denied

Another glitchy take on Phasing - a project exploring our relationships to past and future selves. 7 humans representing 7 liminal states, experiencing aspects of catharsis while hanging from hooks pierced into their flesh. 

Suspension & video by orbgasm
Dark DnB by nllpntr
